---
// v1：视觉占位，不接外部服务。表单禁用，提交不会发送任何数据。
---

<section class="newsletter" aria-labelledby="newsletter-title">
  <p class="eyebrow">Newsletter · 每周案卷</p>
  <h2 class="newsletter__title" id="newsletter-title">让下一份案卷找到你</h2>
  <p class="newsletter__lead text-muted">新案卷上架时，把它送到你的信箱。没有广告，只有谜案。</p>

  <form class="newsletter__form" aria-describedby="newsletter-note" aria-disabled="true">
    <label class="visually-hidden" for="newsletter-email">邮箱地址</label>
    <input
      id="newsletter-email"
      type="email"
      name="email"
      placeholder="you@example.com"
      autocomplete="email"
      disabled
    />
    <button type="button" class="newsletter__btn mono" disabled aria-disabled="true"
      >即将开放</button
    >
  </form>
  <p class="newsletter__note text-muted" id="newsletter-note">订阅功能正在筹备中。</p>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .newsletter__title {
    margin: var(--space-2) 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .newsletter__lead {
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
  }
  .newsletter__form {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 30rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .newsletter__form input {
    flex: 1 1 16rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--color-paper);
    padding: 0.7em 0.9em;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .newsletter__form input:disabled {
    opacity: 0.6;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
  .newsletter__btn {
    padding: 0.7em 1.4em;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gold);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .newsletter__note {
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }
</style>
